{
  "stem": "21089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we knew already that the Germans are coming because the Russian, day and night, kind of was evacuating to Russia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said that-- they said these are just temporary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're regrouping.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're drawing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This what they call it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But finally, many, many people went east, you know, running away from-- especially Jews-- to Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I felt I was running so far, I would not run anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and I stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It came, a order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One of the first order was that Jews couldn't walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Officially said under-- everything was under penalty of death, whatever order was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Lithuanian helped them, the German, If not Lithuania, many Jews would survive and would live.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the Lithuanian were wor-- worst than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Poles was the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is in their blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They hate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they're still hating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I'm not telling this as a theory, but I'm telling you this from practice, what I experienced.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Actually, I had many enemies-- Germans, Poles, Lithuanians, Russians, communists.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was-- and I decided, no, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I will not walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because I saw what happened in Vienna, and at that time, I didn't have a Jewish look, and I could afford to do that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when you see the-- a Jew, and he was hiding, he was-- either was looking forward.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He just eyes down so nobody would recognize him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I felt I would not-- I was fresh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I look straight, sure of himself because when they recognize a Jew, immediately, they kicked, they beat him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- couldn't-- I cannot describe what they did-- just spit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Later, it was orders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They couldn't walk-- walk on a sidewalk, only they couldn't on sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
